ment.uk/resources/1091416/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1091416/answer",,,,,"14","Treasury","Treasury","2019-03-19","London Capital and Finance: Insolvency","1","House of Commons","To ask the Chancellor of the Exchequer, with reference to the collapse of London Capital of Finance, what steps he is taking to prevent investment schemes which engage in mis-selling from trading.","false","Biography information for Chi Onwurah","Newcastle upon Tyne Central","Chi Onwurah","234193"
